extends ../../layout

block content
  h2 YAML
  p YAML has become the most popular data format to configure many tools.  Many DevOps engineers joke that they are YAML engineers because of this.  YAML has a lot of similaries to JSON but also some key differences let's learn more!

  h2 Video - 11 min
  p
    iframe(width="1120",height="630", src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cdLNKUoMc6c", title="YouTube video player", frameborder="0", allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture", allowfullscreen)

  h2 Projects - 15 min
  ol
    li How do you create a comment in YAML? Can you do this in JSON?
    li What data types do JSON and YAML have in common? What data types does only YAML have?
    li Create a file called family.yaml that includes an list with a few fake people and a list of their favorite foods for each person
    li What is an anchor?
    li How do you maintain the formating of a large amount of text in a yaml file?
    li How do you coerce one data type into another in YAML?

  h2 Nice Job!
  p You now know the basics of YAML!
